room_title: Escape room "Sherlock’s Study" by Confundrum Escape Rooms in Idaho Falls
room_address: 763 S Woodruff Ave, Idaho Falls, ID 83404
room_description: In the midst of a murder investigation, Sherlock Holmes has been kidnapped by the very murderer he was trying to catch! Now, it is up to you to piece together the evidence he has left behind in his study. Will you be clever enough to step into Sherlock’s shoes and solve the mystery?
